  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563820/extras/8d3211b73c7af4d29f58b828dc77981b.avif?t=1667321672\" width=610 height=280 /></span><br><br>What's going on in our head!? A lot of thoughts, tasks, memories and emotions.<br>In this bright game \" In my mind” you will plunge into a bright world of adventure, move along the lines beware of dangers and look for a way out.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The main character is an eye, he can move very quickly through the cells, he emits light and energy, but is afraid of saws and sharp blocks with skulls.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563820/extras/44337ea32dd8e57008d57af6f58ce533.poster.avif?t=1667321672\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563820/extras/44337ea32dd8e57008d57af6f58ce533.webm?t=1667321672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563820/extras/44337ea32dd8e57008d57af6f58ce533.mp4?t=1667321672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features of the game:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast moving through lines<br></li><li>Bright main character<br></li><li>Bright level design<br></li><li>Simple puzzles<br></li><li>Achievements for completing levels</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563820/extras/2b94b05428a076c6769866a76168a03c.poster.avif?t=1667321672\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563820/extras/2b94b05428a076c6769866a76168a03c.webm?t=1667321672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563820/extras/2b94b05428a076c6769866a76168a03c.mp4?t=1667321672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
